# Session mode keywords (operator shorthand)

**Language:** Keywords in this table are **English-only tokens**. The operator types them **as written** (e.g. `deps`, `pmo-view`, `study-check`) even when the rest of the message is pt-BR—no Portuguese spellings or synonyms for these cues in rules or committed docs. Chat **narration** may stay pt-BR per **`AGENTS.md`**.

Single-word cues set **session scope**. Prefer **one mode per branch/PR** unless the user explicitly combines tracks.

