| **homelab**           | **Second-environment smoke (manual).** (1) **`read_file`** **`.cursor/rules/homelab-ssh-via-terminal.mdc`** (or **`@homelab-ssh-via-terminal.mdc`** if globs did not load it — rule is **situational**); (2) operator runs **`docs/ops/HOMELAB_VALIDATION.md`** (+ **`.pt_BR.md`** when used). Agent helps with **doc/checklist fixes** or small script tweaks from what you find—not running your hardware.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    | **`PLANS_TODO.md`** (order **–1L**), **`homelab-ssh-via-terminal.mdc`**, **`docs/ops/OPERATOR_AGENT_COLD_START_LADDER.md`** § *Token → rule latch (**`homelab`**)* |
